## Additional Licenses and Attributions

This repository contains code examples and implementations that interface with various AI models and frameworks. Please note the following:

### Model Licenses
- **PyTorch**: BSD-style license (https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/LICENSE)
- **Transformers**: Apache License 2.0 (https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/main/LICENSE)
- **Diffusers**: Apache License 2.0 (https://github.com/huggingface/diffusers/blob/main/LICENSE)

### Model-Specific Terms
When using pre-trained models through this codebase, you must comply with their respective licenses:

- **Google Veo 3**: Subject to Google's Terms of Service and AI Principles
- **Kling AI 2.0**: Subject to Kuaishou's terms and conditions
- **Runway Models**: Subject to Runway's commercial licensing terms
- **HunyuanVideo**: Apache License 2.0 (Tencent open-source)
- **OpenSora**: Apache License 2.0 (open-source)
- **Meta Models**: Custom research license (check individual model pages)

### Dataset Licenses
Sample datasets and examples may be subject to their own licensing terms. Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable licenses when using datasets for training or evaluation.

### Commercial Use
While this codebase is MIT licensed, commercial use of generated content may be subject to the terms of service of the underlying models. Please review each model's licensing terms before commercial deployment.

